- **SG-004 _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates** -- Internal function to manage per-target selector allowlists. Removal of non-existent selector reverts. Duplicate adds are silently ignored (no event). Zero selector cannot be added.
- **SG-005 _call** -- Inherited from Caller.sol. Performs low-level `.call()` with revert bubbling. No ETH value forwarded.
- **SG-006 supportsInterface** -- ERC-165 override combining PausableWithAccessControl interfaces with IReceiver.

